-ray\ntransients, when corrected to the local value, is consistent with the double\nneutron star merger rate density inferred from the detection of GW170817.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Apr 2019 18:00:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-12"}
