on of the emission from M-type star to total emission\ncauses a large variation in the pulsed fraction and the degree of the linear\npolarization along the orbital phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Apr 2019 05:22:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-01"}
