 current developed techniques have limitations\nbecause they are model-based methods, based on ignoring some dynamics, or\nrequiring an indicator of the environment contact. Hence, a robust sensorless\nforce estimation and impedance control scheme is proposed to overcome these\nlimitations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Apr 2019 14:10:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-19"}
